				<ANNOTATION_VALUE>m'hot undz oft mol, nit eyn klap hob ikh gekrogn far far dem vos ikh hob nit vos mir hobn nit gekent araynloyfn arayn- arayngeyn in barak vayl in barak di tir fun barak fun barak hot geven zeyer a shmole,</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
