				<ANNOTATION_VALUE>lager tsvey hot men undz hobn undz gegebn zeyer shlekht esn farshteyt zikh. mir hobn glaykh dershpirt az mir veln do lang nit oyshaltn.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
